            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In hono<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>e<supplied reason="lost">m do</supplied>m<supplied reason="lost">us divinae</supplied> <lb n="2"/>et ob m<supplied reason="lost">erita eius <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Opho<supplied reason="lost">ni</supplied>us <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Pap</abbr><ex>iria</ex></expan> D</supplied>o<supplied reason="lost">mi</supplied>t<supplied reason="lost">ius Priscus</supplied> <lb n="4"/>IIvir c<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ol</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan></supplied> Dac<supplied reason="lost">icae <expan><abbr>pec</abbr><ex>unia</ex></expan> sua fecit <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ocus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Textwiedergabe nach Zeichung (pl. 40, 26). Vom Nymphäum; 14 Fragmente der Inschriftentafel erhalten; die angegebenen Maße sind die rekonstruierten Abmessungen.</p>
            </div>
